<h2>Welcome to the Number API</h2>

<p>The numbers API is a unique service, you can request a number and it will return it!
  Not only that but if you request, we can return it in .xml or .json.</p>

<h4>Try it now!</h4>

<% @random_numbers.each do |number| %>
  <a href="/<%= number %>"><%= number %></a>
<% end %>

